<p>Suburban neighborhoods like Buckhead and Sandy Springs feature larger homes with expansive roof areas ideal for solar installations, while the newer construction in areas like Atlantic Station often incorporates energy-efficient design that maximizes both solar potential and HVAC efficiency. East Atlanta and Grant Park neighborhoods, with their mix of renovated and original homes, present excellent opportunities for integrated solar and HVAC upgrades that can dramatically improve energy efficiency and home values.</p>

